msgid ""
"Labels identify bounded runtime topology; record values, keys, exception "
"text, URLs, checkpoint paths, and Object IDs are never labels. Counter "
"definitions do not include `_total` because Ray's Prometheus exporter adds "
"that suffix."
msgstr "标签用于标识有界的运行时拓扑；记录值、键、异常文本、URL、检查点路径和 Object ID 绝不会成为标签。计数器定义不包含 `_total`，因为 Ray 的 Prometheus exporter 会添加该后缀。"

