msgid ""
"Latencies and batch sizes are histograms rather than last-value gauges. For "
"example, a Prometheus query for operator p95 processing latency is:"
msgstr "延迟和批次大小使用直方图，而不是最新值 gauge。例如，查询算子 p95 处理延迟的 Prometheus 语句为："

msgid "Rows per second can be queried with:"
msgstr "每秒行数可以通过以下语句查询："

msgid ""
"Custom application metrics remain available from `runtime_context."
"metric_group`. Give custom metrics a unit-bearing name and description, "
"reuse the same type and label set for a name, and use histograms for "
"distributions:"
msgstr "自定义应用指标仍可从 `runtime_context.metric_group` 获取。请为自定义指标提供包含单位的名称和说明；同一名称应复用相同的类型和标签集，分布数据应使用直方图："

msgid ""
"Use Ray's Prometheus and Grafana integration for retention, alerting, and "
"cross-job dashboards. Klein snapshots derive short-interval row rates, busy "
"percentage, and backpressure percentage from monotonic task counters without "
"a Prometheus dependency."
msgstr "使用 Ray 的 Prometheus 和 Grafana 集成实现保留、告警和跨作业仪表板。Klein 快照可根据单调任务计数器计算短时间窗口内的行速率、忙碌百分比和反压百分比，不依赖 Prometheus。"

msgid ""
"For symptom-oriented interpretation, see [Performance tuning](performance-"
"tuning.md) and [Troubleshooting](troubleshooting.md)."
msgstr "按症状理解指标的方法，请参阅[性能调优](performance-tuning.md)和[故障排除](troubleshooting.md)。"

msgid "State publication architecture"
msgstr "状态发布架构"

msgid "The standalone integration uses only a small Ray actor surface:"
msgstr "独立集成只使用很小的 Ray actor 接口面："

msgid ""
"A streaming `JobClient` registers its `JobManager` with one detached, zero-"
"CPU state actor on the Ray head node."
msgstr "流处理 `JobClient` 会把自己的 `JobManager` 注册到 Ray head 节点上一个分离、零 CPU 的状态 actor。"

msgid ""
"The state actor refreshes immutable snapshots concurrently and keeps the "
"last good snapshot for temporary actor outages and terminal history."
msgstr "状态 actor 会并发刷新不可变快照，并保留最近一次良好快照，以应对临时 actor 中断和终止作业历史。"

msgid ""
"`list_job_snapshots`, `get_job_snapshot`, `rescale_operator`, and "
"`cancel_job` expose a stable client API for CLIs, dashboards, and automation."
msgstr "`list_job_snapshots`、`get_job_snapshot`、`rescale_operator` 和 `cancel_job` 为 CLI、仪表板和自动化提供稳定客户端 API。"

msgid ""
"The bundled HTTP page is one adapter over this API. An eventual native Ray "
"Dashboard contribution can reuse the same boundary without moving scheduling "
"state into the dashboard process."
msgstr "内置 HTTP 页面是该 API 上的一个适配器。未来的原生 Ray Dashboard 贡献可以复用同一边界，无需将调度状态移入仪表板进程。"
